src directory contain source codes of bdd apply and relational product functions

mc.c contain model checking algorithms implemented as per problem statement 1.

blib-test.c contain sample test case of 2-bit counter.

blib.h is an interface to library functions in src directory.

make command will compile all files aling with blib-test.c and create executable blib-test

This project was created as a part of course MCSV in CMI